window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>Music star Silver Lawson has it allâ€”except her freedom.</b></p> <p>Thrust into the spotlight six years ago at the tender age of sixteen, pop sensation Silver is the envy of teenage girls all over the globe. But beneath the public persona lies a woman whose demons run deep.</p> <p>Royal Marine veteran Cruise \"Crew\" Garrett only has to survive three months guarding the diva who pushes buttons he didn't know he possessed. As he peels back the layers to the real woman beneath her superstar image, he uncovers a well of dark secrets amid a sickening past.</p> <p>Crew has never run from trouble in his life, but saving Silver might cost him more than he's willing to pay.</p> <p>The question is, how far will he go for the woman who has stolen his heart?</p>"; 
